gujarati.context:
Victory to the unbound, unending, and infinite; 
Victory to the great, unmatched, and timeless; 
Victory to the blazing, limitless, and boundless; 
Victory to the imperishable, endless, and infinite.

Here are the translations:

Golokadi dhaam kahiye jeh, yog siddhiyo kave chhe teh;
Tethi vahala munie tume bahu, satya manjyo vaat e sah.

becomes:

Declare it to Goloka's abode, whoever has attained spiritual perfection; 
Therefore, the wise monks, you are many, who speak the truth and are truthful.

Here are the translations:

Those equal to Shiva and Brahma, you make sacrifices of service;
This and that is ours, but you are my soulmate.

Here are the translations:

Arjano narayana narbhroat, eni ame na khavevaa vat;
Chare varne chare aashram, teene tyagee diidha nij dharma.
